snippet.title: Shumi Come Home - Official Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Shumi Come Home's latest trailer shows off gameplay from a variety of levels and showcases the game that lets you play as a tiny little mushroom who's lost in the forest and can't find its way home. Explore unique areas freely at your own pace, chat with friendly inhabitants, and take on different adventures to get back home!

#GameTrailers #Gaming
